org.gcn.plinguacore.simulator

Class AbstractSelectionExecutionSimulator

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.gcn.plinguacore.simulator.AbstractSimulator
      • org.gcn.plinguacore.simulator.AbstractSelectionExecutionSimulator
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, ISimulator
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    CellLikeSimulator, SpikingSimulator, TissueLikeSimulator, TSCSSimulator

    public abstract class AbstractSelectionExecutionSimulator
extends AbstractSimulator
    An abstract class for simulators which execute simulation steps in three microsteps: init step, select rules for the whole configuration, execute rules for the whole configuration
